<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226711>
    dc:description "FIGURES 36 – 42. Eukoenenia sendrai sp. nov., holotype. 36, frontal organ, dorsal view; 37, lateral organ, dorsal view; 38, coxa I; 39, coxa II; 40, coxa IV; 41, coxa III; 42, pedipalp coxa. Thick coxal setae represented with a thicker line and a terminal spine. Scale bars 36 – 37 = 50 µm; 38 – 42 = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/226711/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226712>
    dc:description "FIGURES 43 – 44. Eukoenenia sendrai sp. nov., holotype. 43, basitarsi 3 – 4, leg I; 44, basitarsus, leg IV. Scale bar = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/226712/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226713>
    dc:description "FIGURES 45 – 46. Eukoenenia sendrai sp. nov., holotype opisthosoma. 46, dorsal view; 47, ventral view. Scale bar 200 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/226713/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226714>
    dc:description "FIGURE 47. Eukoenenia sendrai sp. nov., holotype female, genital region. Scale bar = 50 µm." ;
